main event: Ground personnel within a 5-mile radius visually sighted 2 Air Force jets fly over ice and disappear behind hills.
interesting points: The sighting occurred on September 15, 1960, and lasted about 30 minutes., Multiple witnesses were ground personnel observing the Air Force jets., The report questioned the accuracy of the object description., Various conclusions were drawn including it possibly being an illusion or a balloon., There was a lack of confirmation and evidence regarding the sighting.
